Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 06 of Feet MRI
When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then Finding dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Charcot Foot' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Characterization I' tab is enabled and preselected
And 'Characterization II' tab is enabled

And 'Bone marrow edema' checkbox is enabled
And 'Joint effusion' checkbox is enabled
And 'Joint destruction' checkbox is enabled
And '(subchondral) microfracture' checkbox is enabled
And 'Fracture' checkbox is enabled
And 'Dislocation' checkbox is enabled
And 'Subchondral cysts' checkbox is enabled
And 'Loose Fragment' checkbox is enabled
And 'Osteomyelitis' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Bone marrow edema' checkbox
Then 'Periarticular accentuation' checkbox is enabled
And 'In the metatarsotarsal joints' checkbox is enabled
And 'In the metatarsophalangeal joints' checkbox is enabled
And 'Area 1' checkbox is enabled
And 'Area 2' checkbox is enabled
And 'Area 3' checkbox is enabled
And 'Area 4' checkbox is enabled
And 'Area 5' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Joint destruction' checkbox
Then 'Area 1' checkbox is enabled
And 'Area 2' checkbox is enabled
And 'Area 3' checkbox is enabled
And 'Area 4' checkbox is enabled
And 'Area 5' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Fracture' checkbox
Then 'Navicular bone' checkbox is enabled
When I select 'Navicular bone' checkbox
Then 'Fragmentation' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Dislocation' checkbox
Then 'Metatarsals cranial & lateral (Lisfranc joint)' checkbox is enabled
And 'Collapse of the longitudinal arch' checkbox is enabled
And 'Plantarflexion of the talus' checkbox is enabled
And 'Navicular bone to cranial & medial' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Collapse of the longitudinal arch' checkbox
Then 'Rockerbottom-deformity' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Subchondral cysts' checkbox
Then 'Lisfranc joint' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Osteomyelitis' checkbox
Then 'Ghost sign on T1w images' checkbox is enabled
And 'Cuboid bone' checkbox is enabled
And 'Cuneiform bones' checkbox is enabled
And 'Metatarsals' checkbox is enabled
